==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Helpmeet
<hw>Help"meet`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Helpmate</er>.]</ety> <def>A wife; a helpmate.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The Lord God created Adam, . . . and afterwards, on his finding
the want of a <qex>helpmeet</qex>, caused him to sleep, and took one of
his ribs and thence made woman.</q> <rj><qau>J. H.
Newman.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Helter-skelter</ent>⟦br⟧
